comments: Siakam (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position and does not deliver contact to Dragic (MIA).
Winslow (MIA) makes contact to the body of Siakam (TOR) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) does not deliver contact to Lowry (TOR) during the pick and he legally rolls to the basket.
Gasol (TOR) makes contact to the arm of Johnson (MIA) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Adebayo (MIA) delivers body contact to Leonard (TOR) that affects his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Dragic (MIA) splits his feet.
[Observable in enhanced video] Leonard (TOR) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Siakam (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Wade (MIA).
Lowry (TOR) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Johnson (MIA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Leonard (TOR) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.

As the Heat are ready to inbound, the official sounds his whistle to start the throw-in but Waiters (MIA) steps onto the floor before the ball is at his disposal and the Heat begin their offensive set.  Waiters then steps out of bounds to receive the throw-in and the official gives him the ball to inbound.
Green (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position on Adebayo (MIA) at the start of the drive.
RAR shows Gasol (TOR) establishes himself in a legal guarding position and jumps vertically to contest the shot attempt by Johnson (MIA), who jumps slightly forward and initiates the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact with the ball and incidental contact with Lowry (TOR) that does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
